{"tid":823726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵廣播：大埔和上水免費穿梭巴士服務未能提供","createTime":"2018-09-17T00:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T01:25:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c1aa0aad5aa426a761f59bdbd50a9ecec28b0d","tid":823726,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"港鐵廣播指，由大埔墟站至上水站之間有樹木倒塌，架空電纜受損，令服務受影響。受路面狀況影響，目前來往大埔和上水的免費穿梭巴士服務未能提供。<br />\n<br />\n在粉嶺港鐵站，有市民說，排隊近一小時才知道港鐵暫未能提供接駁巴士服務，令她感不滿。她說，要到黃埔上班，上司已多次催促她返公司，但目前沒有巴士或港鐵等服務，只能繼續等接駁巴士。<br />\n<br />\n亦有市民說，要到將軍澳上班，找不到的士，亦沒有港鐵及巴士服務，現時亦未能靠接駁巴士前往上班，認為港鐵應及早通知。"},{"pid":"a2a3ce1b7fbc9347b255bfea7e5bc171eeceb156","tid":823726,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418421-20180917.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418421-20180917.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jswbPQnabvIpAkxVJWlMC5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=15c7e162\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418421-20180917.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=96010c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418421-20180917.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f9e705085a8d9babc53751a0f68445bdccef4e8b","tid":823726,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"住新界把撚咩，住大灣區就返到工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4157a1adaf92d83913847aa368d3d28c97502ce1","tid":823726,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 她說，要到黃埔上班，<span style=\"color: red;\">上司已多次催促她返公司</span>，但目前沒有巴士或港鐵等服務，只能繼續等接駁巴士。</blockquote>閪工，開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /